{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even if you-- if you say doesn't-- didn't exist, you know it did exist, and you know it-- it was possible and it was done to human beings, and it was done to children.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not done in war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was done to just normal civil population.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after they-- we were-- all the time we were standing around in nothing, or they didn't even put numbers on us anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just threw some clothes on us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember I couldn't stand the color purple for a few years, because I got just one little-- you might call it a dress.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a summer dress of a purple color, and that's all I went through October, November, December.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- You had nothing underneath?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have any--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got some-- we got some shoes, because we had to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not even-- they were-- I think they were wooden clogs or something, but I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was not so comfortable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, you can imagine, it's like-- Poland is like Russia and it's very cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you don't feel it, and you survive with and you don't get influenza.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't get sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You cannot afford to get sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, you are almost [INAUDIBLE] before to coldness.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I know now that I sleep with open window and everything, and everyone says, are you crazy?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I need air.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's really unbelievable if you remember it, or if you think about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After three years of-- even more then, because the war years were all not so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Actually, from '38 to '42, you were not so well-nourished.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
